<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She's had an exciting week after celebrating her 39th birthday.</p>

<p>And Ashley Roberts appeared in good spirits on Thursday as she made a glamorous exit from her Heart Radio duties at Global Studios in London.</p>

<p>The Pussycat Dolls star looked effortlessly chic as she showcased her toned figure in a polka dot shirred top and matching patterned ruffled mini skirt.</p>

<p>Chic: Ashley Roberts appeared in good spirits on Thursday as she made a glamorous exit from her Heart Radio duties at Global Studios in London</p>

<p>Adding some sophisticated touches and dressing for the September weather, Ashley opted for a striped knitted cardigan. </p>

<p>Ashley finished her ensemble with a pair of black cat eye sunglasses, a studded Yves Saint Laurent handbag and white platform trainers.</p>

<p>The former Strictly star styled her blonde locks into a ponytail and left the front strands loose for a soft finish, she added a slick of radiant make-up.</p>

<p>Ashley appeared in great spirits as she put on an animated display while leaving the studios in Leicester Square.</p>

<p>Sophisticated! The Pussycat Dolls star looked effortlessly chic as she showcased her toned figure in a polka dot shirred top and matching patterned ruffled mini skirt</p>

<p>Tres glamorous! Adding some sophisticated touches and dressing for the September weather, Ashley opted for a striped knitted cardigan</p>

<p>On Monday night, Ashley stepped out for dinner at La Famiglia in Chelsea to mark the milestone of her 39th birthday.  </p>

<p>Earlier in the day, the singing sensation treated her Instagram followers to a racy new bikini snap to mark the occasion.  </p>

<p>The blonde beauty showed off her incredible physique in a matching two-piece while posing for the playful image. </p>

<p>Details: Ashley finished her ensemble with a pair of black cat eye sunglasses, a studded Yves Saint Laurent handbag and white platform trainers</p>

<p>What a beauty: The former Strictly star styled her blonde locks into a ponytail and left the front strands loose for a soft finish, she added a slick of radiant make-up</p>

<p>Referencing her birthday and Britain's unseasonably warm September weather in an accompanying caption, she wrote: 'Ring Ring: Alexa says it’s 30 degrees and my birthday hunni’s. Thank you for all your lovely messages!!!'  </p>

<p>The post prompted an inevitable wave of positive comments from fans, among them former Strictly Come Dancing champion Stacey Dooley, who wrote: 'WELL WELL WELL, happy bday sis.' </p>

<p>Earlier that day Ashley admitted she had been spoiled with cakes, champagne and cards from her extended family at Heart Radio after turning up for her role as showbiz correspondent. </p>

<p>The singer shared an Instagram video showing a caterpillar cake, a sumptuous-looking white chocolate creation, a bottle of Taittinger champagne and Hypnotiq fruit liqueur to kick off her day of celebrations.  </p>

<p>Happy: Ashley appeared in great spirits as she put on an animated display while leaving the studios in Leicester Square</p>
